# Wofi configuration
#
# Wofi uses a simple key=value syntax.  See `man wofi` for all
# available options【693684191083146†L20-L154】.  The colours file referenced here
# comes from Pywal/Matugen; if it doesn’t exist, Wofi falls back to
# default colours【65769973931695†L46-L139】.

show = drun
